    <mxCell id="4" value="&lt;b&gt;Refined GLIM&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Same architecture&lt;br&gt;Parameters optimised via LHS&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Improvements:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;50–85% error reduction&lt;br&gt;Delayed onset of failure&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Residual limitations:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;Scan-matching instability persists&lt;br&gt;Occasional catastrophic failure&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#b8860b&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Error: 0.61–3.62 %/m&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
