    <mxCell id="5" value="&lt;b&gt;Proposed Method&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;GNSS-augmented factor graph&lt;br&gt;LiDAR–inertial + sparse GNSS&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Improvements:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;97–99% error reduction&lt;br&gt;Near-deterministic behaviour&lt;br&gt;No catastrophic failure observed&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Key property:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;0.65–0.78% GNSS utilisation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#82b366&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Error: 0.015–0.050 %/m&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
